title: Hong Kong And Singapore Lead Asia's Drive To Cash In On Crypto Boom
description: Hong Kong and Singapore are the front-runners in a push by Asian governments to become cryptocurrency hubs as they look to capitalise on the global resurgence of the sector thanks to the support of US President Donald Trump.
